      "span_text": "In accordance with Landis and Koch, we interpreted ICC values as follows: >0.80 was almost perfect, 0.61-0.80 was substantial, 0.41-0.60 was moderate, 0.21-0.40 was fair, 0.20-0.00 was slight, and <0.00 was poor"
